										<width>70</width>
									</dimensions>
								</extent>
								<foliation>
									<p>231 folios (+ 3 unfoliated paper flyleaves at the beginning and 4 at the end). </p>
								</foliation>
								<collation>
									<p>Quires of mostly 16 leaves each.</p>
								</collation>
							</supportDesc>
							<layoutDesc>
								<layout columns="1" ruledLines="14 18" writtenLines="14 18">
									<p>Uniform layout. </p>
									<p>Visible hard-point ruling.</p>
									<p>Horizontal catchwords on every page. </p>
									<p>Initial words given in larger characters.</p>
									<p>Running titles.</p>
									<p>Original foliation in the upper left-hand margin of each recto.</p>
									<p>Folio 1 is a title page.</p>
								</layout>
							</layoutDesc>
